T1  - Car Pool Systems in Railroad Transportation: Mathematical Models
AU  - Avi-Itzhak, B.
AU  - Benn, B. A.
AU  - Powell, B. A.
Y1  - 1967/05/01
PY  - 1967
DA  - 1967/05/01
